{"title":"IntoxicacionParacetamol","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Urgencias/IntoxicacionParacetamol iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Intoxicación por Paracetamol en Urgencias","guid":"UMfdmHra36uIYqKadCTUug","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Analgésico más usado en el mundo sin receta médica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Causa más frecuente de falla hepática aguda en países desarrollados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"EE.UU. → ~50.000 consultas/año por sobredosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Mortalidad global 0.4% en sobredosis tratadas oportunamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Chile → disponible en farmacias y automedicación frecuente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"73% mujeres en series de urgencias (Codinach-Martín 2022)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"81% de ingestas por intención voluntaria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"ADULTO MAYOR → mayor riesgo por polifarmacia y automedicación crónica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"Ingesta repetida supraterapéutica → presentación insidiosa en AM","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"0","text":"Farmacología y\\NToxicocinética","guid":"qTr47a2bjGtjx5Lrm67qgg","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"Dosis terapéutica → 10-15 mg/kg cada 6-8h (máx 4g/día)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"En AM → considerar máx 2g/día si fragilidad, desnutrición o hepatopatía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"Absorción GI rápida → peak 30-60 min (liberación inmediata)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"11","text":"Formulación de liberación extendida → peak retardado 2-4h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"11","text":"Vida media normal 2-4h → prolongada en AM y hepatopatía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"11","text":"Metabolismo\\Nhepático","guid":"vUntKxEpyWZMgfQbHSuNmA","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"90% conjugación (glucuronidación + sulfatación) → metabolitos no tóxicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"5-10% CYP2E1 → NAPQI (N-acetil-p-benzoquinoneimina) → METABOLITO TÓXICO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"NAPQI detoxificado por GLUTATIÓN → conjugado no tóxico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"17","text":"Saturación de vías de conjugación → mayor producción de NAPQI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"11","text":"Umbral de\\Ntoxicidad","guid":"Njduiu0ZeGPWXwEOtPtoRQ","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Aguda → >=150 mg/kg o >=7.5g en adultos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"Repetida supraterapéutica → >4g/día por >=2 días","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"FACTORES QUE\\NREDUCEN EL UMBRAL","guid":"78auEdnhBn2a6WvrrRX_iw","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"Alcoholismo crónico → inducción CYP2E1 + depleción glutatión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"Desnutrición/ayuno → depleción de glutatión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"Fármacos inductores CYP → isoniazida, rifampicina, anticonvulsivantes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"25","text":"Enfermedad hepática crónica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"25","text":"ADULTO MAYOR → menor masa hepática, menor glutatión basal","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología de\\Nla Hepatotoxicidad","guid":"GVdEVs9n2LContHcrABUcw","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"Fase I (0-24h) → generación masiva de NAPQI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"Depleción de glutatión >70% → NAPQI libre se une a proteínas celulares","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"Daño mitocondrial → disfunción oxidativa → ACIDOSIS LÁCTICA PRECOZ","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"31","text":"Necrosis hepatocitaria centrolobulillar (zona 3)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"31","text":"Toxicidad intestinal directa →\\NIFABP elevado (Perananthan 2024)","guid":"YTFUlVXxttGZVF0MK3WGVA","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Hiperlactatemia precoz (<12h) correlaciona con daño intestinal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"Impacto en farmacocinética de coingestas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"31","text":"Progresión a falla hepática fulminante sin tratamiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"31","text":"Falla multiorgánica → coagulopatía, encefalopatía, IRA, edema cerebral","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"0","text":"Presentación\\NClínica por Fases","guid":"GM0fpzkAcue3fuWQZBGoCg","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Fase I → 0 a 24\\Nhoras post-ingesta","guid":"RVdAv9BOG4rr9dJ8JzByIA","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"Asintomático o síntomas inespecíficos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"Náuseas, vómitos, malestar general, diaforesis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"EN AM → confusión puede ser síntoma inicial (BUSCAR ACTIVAMENTE)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"42","text":"Laboratorio normal o mínimamente alterado","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"41","text":"Fase II → 24 a 72\\Nhoras","guid":"6TqYU0wD_xejenrKmsOl6Q","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"Dolor en hipocondrio derecho","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"Elevación de transaminasas (pico 72h) → AST/ALT >1000 UI/L","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"Elevación de bilirrubina, prolongación de INR/TP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"47","text":"Oliguria → inicio de compromiso renal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"47","text":"EN AM → deterioro funcional agudo, delirium sobreagregado","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"41","text":"Fase III → 72 a 96 horas\\N(FASE CRÍTICA)","guid":"tlis8_UkT3qWjjjGaLJMeA","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"Falla hepática fulminante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"Encefalopatía hepática grado III-IV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"53","text":"Coagulopatía severa → INR >6","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"53","text":"Acidosis metabólica → lactato >3.5 mmol/L","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"53","text":"Falla renal → NTA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"53","text":"Hipoglicemia → reservas hepáticas agotadas","guid":"tYMzw8lqN2wB1tJkBaPbMA","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"53","text":"MORTALIDAD MÁXIMA en esta fase","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"41","text":"Fase IV → 4 a 14 días","guid":"vfkJGZIOyvmZUWxklGvipQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"Resolución si sobrevive fase III","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"Regeneración hepática completa en la mayoría","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"Recuperación histológica en 3-4 semanas","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación\\Nen Urgencias","guid":"kkMcAKelRsqx2eJOfOkrUQ","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"TRIAGE → sospecha en TODO paciente con ingesta voluntaria o sobredosis analgésica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"Anamnesis\\NDIRIGIDA","guid":"kCesae9oujt26DPV5aYa1A","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Hora exacta de ingesta (CRUCIAL para nomograma)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Cantidad ingerida (mg/kg peso real)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"Formulación → liberación inmediata vs extendida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"67","text":"Ingesta única vs repetida supraterapéutica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"67","text":"Coingestas → opioides, anticolinérgicos, alcohol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"67","text":"Intención → voluntaria vs accidental","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"67","text":"EN AM → revisar TODOS los medicamentos del hogar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"67","text":"Preguntar por productos combinados (codeína + paracetamol, tramadol + paracetamol)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"65","text":"Laboratorio INICIAL\\N(a las 4h post-ingesta\\No al ingreso si >4h)","guid":"zm0EVMNP3SnUx_cchSQt9A","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"Nivel sérico de paracetamol → OBLIGATORIO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"AST/ALT → basal y seriado cada 12-24h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"INR/TP → marcador de síntesis hepática","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"76","text":"Creatinina/BUN → función renal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"76","text":"Electrolitos, glicemia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"76","text":"Lactato → marcador precoz de severidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"76","text":"Gases arteriales/venosos → acidosis metabólica","guid":"mHBT7JJt_T7DMvQSBtpc4w","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"76","text":"Lipasa → coingestión o daño pancreático","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"76","text":"Test de embarazo en mujeres en edad fértil","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"65","text":"Nivel sérico de\\Nparacetamol","guid":"WY5ZSeZcjwYnTJqKPl7KUA","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"Medir a las 4h post-ingesta (antes NO es interpretable)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"Si hora desconocida → medir al ingreso y repetir en 4h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"Nivel >10 mcg/mL con hora desconocida → tratar con NAC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"86","text":"NOMOGRAMA\\NRUMACK-MATTHEW\\NREVISADO (Dart 2023)","guid":"-TA7thbABmJ3_8H16n7KQQ","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"Línea de tratamiento a 150 mcg/mL a las 4h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"Línea de ALTO RIESGO → reemplaza término \"ingesta masiva\"","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"Usar solo en ingesta aguda única 4-24h post-ingesta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"90","text":"NO USAR si ingesta repetida, hora desconocida o >24h","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"0","text":"Nomograma\\NRumack-Matthew\\NRevisado","guid":"vQFOZzW47vqg194pCo4eCg","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"Ingesta aguda definida como presentación 4-24h post-sobredosis (Dart 2023)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"Eje X → tiempo desde ingesta (4-24h)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"Eje Y → concentración sérica paracetamol (escala log)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"95","text":"Línea de tratamiento → 150 mcg/mL a 4h, 37.5 mcg/mL a 12h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"95","text":"POR SOBRE la línea → INICIAR NAC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"95","text":"POR DEBAJO → observación si asintomático y AST/ALT normales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"95","text":"Línea de ALTO RIESGO →\\Nconcentraciones muy elevadas","guid":"USQItSRULxob-DKrTT2Q9g","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"Indica necesidad de monitorización intensificada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"Considerar fomepizole como adyuvante","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"95","text":"LIMITACIONES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"No aplica a ingesta repetida supraterapéutica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"No aplica si hora de ingesta desconocida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"No aplica >24h post-ingesta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"105","text":"Coingestas que retrasan absorción → pueden subestimar riesgo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"105","text":"EN AM → usar con precaución, umbral más bajo de sospecha","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"111","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"Descontaminación\\NGI","guid":"v68Xf3SOArGiTh4gcOZd5g","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"Carbón activado 1g/kg (máx 50g) → PRIMERA LÍNEA si <4h post-ingesta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"Mayor beneficio <2h, útil hasta 4h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"Reduce absorción de paracetamol significativamente (Cochrane 2018)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"CONTRAINDICACIONES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"Vía aérea no protegida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"116","text":"Íleo, perforación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"116","text":"Coingestión de cáusticos o hidrocarburos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"112","text":"EN AM → evaluar riesgo aspiración (disfagia, deterioro conciencia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"112","text":"Lavado gástrico → no recomendado de rutina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"112","text":"Ipecacuana → NO recomendada","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"123","parent":"111","text":"N-ACETILCISTEÍNA (NAC) →\\NANTÍDOTO DE ELECCIÓN","guid":"0VvvV7OtJ3Fs1c6JY8-Rtg","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"Mecanismo → precursor de glutatión, detoxifica NAPQI directamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"123","text":"Efectividad cercana al 100% si se inicia <8h post-ingesta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"123","text":"Beneficio demostrado incluso en falla hepática establecida (Cochrane 2018)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"123","text":"PROTOCOLO IV\\NTRADICIONAL\\N(21h, 3 bolsas)","guid":"ZsQK2peZ2oEZ9E0iOfVXTw","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"Bolsa 1 → 150 mg/kg en 200mL D5W en 1h (carga)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"127","text":"Bolsa 2 → 50 mg/kg en 500mL D5W en 4h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"127","text":"Bolsa 3 → 100 mg/kg en 1000mL D5W en 16h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"127","text":"Dosis total → 300 mg/kg en 21h","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"123","text":"PROTOCOLO SNAP\\N(12h, 2 bolsas) →\\NEMERGENTE","guid":"K9KJmbTCmYGmP1S0Bzt4vw","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"Scottish and Newcastle Acetylcysteine Protocol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"Bolsa 1 → 200 mg/kg en 500mL D5W en 2h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"132","text":"Bolsa 2 → 100 mg/kg en 1000mL D5W en 10h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"132","text":"Dosis total → 300 mg/kg en 12h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"132","text":"VENTAJAS → menos efectos adversos (Supervía 2025)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"132","text":"Menor estancia en urgencias (17.8h vs 25.9h, p=0.001)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"132","text":"Menor estancia hospitalaria (2.6d vs 4.4d, p=0.019)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"132","text":"Misma efectividad que protocolo tradicional","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"123","text":"PROTOCOLO 2 BOLSAS\\N/ 20h → alternativa","guid":"oYbxmieOtjQ1HnQKTTWbqA","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"Combina bolsa 1+2 del tradicional en una sola infusión de 4h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"Menos reacciones anafilactoides (Cole 2023)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"141","text":"Sin diferencia en hepatotoxicidad vs 3 bolsas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"123","text":"NAC ORAL (72h) →\\Nalternativa cuando\\NIV no disponible","guid":"v6BcZxSavX64NIAhZFEUFw","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"Carga 140 mg/kg oral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"Luego 70 mg/kg cada 4h por 17 dosis adicionales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"145","text":"Mayor incidencia de vómitos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"123","text":"CRITERIOS PARA\\NSUSPENDER NAC","guid":"6hw9xbVAMcGqdTEfIJJTvQ","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"Paracetamol sérico indetectable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"AST/ALT normales o en descenso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"149","text":"INR <2.0","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"149","text":"Paciente clínicamente bien","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"154","parent":"123","text":"REACCIONES\\NADVERSAS A\\NNAC IV","guid":"v8rlQRVCf28xgy-gV2aQmw","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"Anafilactoides en 8.2% (Yarema 2018)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"154","text":"95% ocurren en primeras 5h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"154","text":"75% cutáneas → urticaria, prurito","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"154","text":"Factores de riesgo → sexo femenino, nivel bajo de paracetamol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"154","text":"Manejo → reducir velocidad de infusión + antihistamínicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"154","text":"NO suspender NAC por reacción leve → riesgo hepatotoxicidad > riesgo reacción","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"161","parent":"123","text":"EN AM → ajustar volumen de dilución si IC o sobrecarga hídrica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"123","text":"Peso >100kg → usar peso real hasta 100kg, luego calcular con 100kg","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"111","text":"FOMEPIZOLE →\\NADYUVANTE EN CASOS\\NGRAVES","guid":"hg7jHbfAC8WBzBrgsDDAfA","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"Inhibidor de CYP2E1 → reduce producción de NAPQI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"Inhibidor de daño oxidativo mediado por JNK","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"163","text":"INDICACIONES\\N(Chen 2025)","guid":"HaM_5DRGTgMfcS_4H-0EYQ","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"Ingesta de alto riesgo con presentación tardía >8h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"Sobredosis masiva (>500 mg/kg)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"166","text":"Evidencia de hepatotoxicidad a pesar de NAC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"166","text":"Considerar en espera de trasplante","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"163","text":"Dosis → 15 mg/kg IV carga, luego 10 mg/kg cada 12h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"163","text":"Resultados favorables en laboratorio y clínica cuando se usa con NAC","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"111","text":"Tratamiento extracorpóreo\\N(EXTRIP 2014)","guid":"1KGpOVEwjfympGinZIkgzA","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"NAC es tratamiento principal → ECTR NO indicado en mayoría","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"INDICACIONES\\NESPECÍFICAS","guid":"Rs2JgVtBe-ple0zTcdi4rw","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"Paracetamol >1000 mg/L sin NAC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"Paracetamol >700 mg/L + disfunción mitocondrial sin NAC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"175","text":"Paracetamol >900 mg/L + disfunción mitocondrial CON NAC","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"179","parent":"173","text":"Disfunción mitocondrial → acidosis metabólica + alteración de conciencia PRECOZ","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"173","text":"Hemodiálisis intermitente → modalidad preferida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"173","text":"Paracetamol ES dializable (PM 151 Da, baja unión a proteínas)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"0","text":"Criterios de\\NGravedad y\\NTrasplante","guid":"F_Z0Hcx7ZF_5pp28jz-SSQ","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"CRITERIOS DE KING'S COLLEGE\\N(paracetamol)","guid":"7E2FC3CHfpW6qObi7RrrdA","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"pH <7.3 después de reanimación con fluidos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"183","text":"O los 3 siguientes\\NJUNTOS","guid":"52jZuK6RFr_t5crz0ayEFA","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"INR >6.5 (TP >100 seg)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"Creatinina >3.4 mg/dL (300 µmol/L)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"185","text":"Encefalopatía hepática grado III-IV","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"189","parent":"182","text":"Lactato >3.5 mmol/L a las 4h o >3.0 mmol/L a las 12h post-reanimación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"182","text":"Factores de mal\\Npronóstico adicionales","guid":"Hi6-InaT9R98qRUk732ukQ","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"Edad >40 años o <10 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"190","text":"Intervalo ingesta-NAC >24h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"190","text":"Nivel de paracetamol excesivamente alto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"190","text":"Falla renal concomitante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"190","text":"EN AM → fragilidad (CFS >=5) impacta decisión de trasplante","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones\\NGeriátricas Específicas","guid":"opuACAC0LIRjClc4OZ8MeA","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"FARMACOCINÉTICA\\NALTERADA EN AM","guid":"SXOJaY41J216SfTCuLtSmA","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"Menor masa hepática → menor metabolismo de primer paso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"Menor flujo hepático → vida media prolongada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"197","text":"Menor reserva de glutatión → umbral tóxico más bajo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"197","text":"Polifarmacia → inductores CYP2E1 más frecuentes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"197","text":"Función renal disminuida → menor clearance de metabolitos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"203","parent":"196","text":"PRESENTACIÓN\\NATÍPICA","guid":"iJgn87aeMFycXvi4_7oksw","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"Síntomas inespecíficos → confusión, anorexia, debilidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"203","text":"Delirium como PRIMERA MANIFESTACIÓN","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"203","text":"Dolor abdominal puede estar ausente o minimizado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"203","text":"Ingesta repetida supraterapéutica → MÁS COMÚN que sobredosis aguda","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"203","text":"Automedicación con múltiples productos que contienen paracetamol","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"209","parent":"196","text":"EVALUACIÓN\\NESPECÍFICA","guid":"_PBNP6chyVQDeDJqHUoZOg","children":[{"id":"210","parent":"209","text":"Revisar TODOS los medicamentos (incluidos OTC y combinados)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"209","text":"VGI abreviada en urgencias → funcionalidad basal, cognición, fragilidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"209","text":"CFS para estratificar pronóstico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"209","text":"Evaluar red de apoyo → riesgo de sobredosis accidental recurrente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"209","text":"Calcular dosis por peso real (sarcopenia → peso puede subestimar riesgo)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"215","parent":"196","text":"MANEJO\\NADAPTADO","guid":"AF6bKQQhubqwk1EKvGXsKQ","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"NAC → ajustar volumen de dilución en IC/ERC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"215","text":"Monitorizar balance hídrico estricto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"215","text":"Carbón activado → evaluar riesgo aspiración cuidadosamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"215","text":"Evitar opioides en manejo de síntomas → riesgo delirium","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"215","text":"Deprescripción post-evento → revisar necesidad real de paracetamol crónico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"215","text":"Considerar máximo 2g/día en frágil, desnutrido o hepatopatía","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"196","text":"DECISIONES DE\\NPROPORCIONALIDAD","guid":"YT__781Gk1IbfTKG9bEtUw","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"CFS >=7 + falla hepática fulminante → discusión de LET","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"Trasplante hepático → evaluar caso a caso según funcionalidad premórbida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"222","text":"Cuidados paliativos → considerar si no es candidato a trasplante","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"226","parent":"0","text":"Disposición y\\NSeguimiento","guid":"7Rrz8YlLw6qQ-UBNbJd5Cw","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"ALTA desde urgencias\\N→ criterios","guid":"fFgKkLsJbiP5NPGcqPbp2w","children":[{"id":"228","parent":"227","text":"Nivel de paracetamol bajo línea de tratamiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"227","text":"AST/ALT normales a las 12-24h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"227","text":"NAC completada sin complicaciones","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"227","text":"Evaluación psiquiátrica si ingesta voluntaria (OBLIGATORIA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"227","text":"Plan de seguimiento con hepatología si hubo hepatotoxicidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"233","parent":"226","text":"HOSPITALIZACIÓN\\N→ criterios","guid":"YqM4F2guwIiPCmQpl4cWZg","children":[{"id":"234","parent":"233","text":"Nivel sobre línea de tratamiento en nomograma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"233","text":"AST/ALT elevadas o en ascenso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"233","text":"INR prolongado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"233","text":"Síntomas de hepatotoxicidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"233","text":"Ingesta de alto riesgo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"233","text":"Ingesta repetida con transaminasas alteradas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"240","parent":"226","text":"UCI → criterios","guid":"uzMz8lguDh-jni_yRJsh4g","children":[{"id":"241","parent":"240","text":"Falla hepática aguda → INR >2, encefalopatía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"240","text":"Acidosis metabólica → lactato >3.5 mmol/L","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"240","text":"Falla renal aguda","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"240","text":"Coagulopatía severa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"240","text":"Evaluación para trasplante hepático","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"246","parent":"226","text":"EN AM → considerar\\Nhospitalización con\\Numbral más bajo","guid":"cBTkY0Ak9tSydC1jCr-I4w","children":[{"id":"247","parent":"246","text":"Mayor riesgo de complicaciones","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"246","text":"Necesidad de VGI completa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"246","text":"Evaluación social si sobredosis accidental recurrente","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"250","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClínicas","guid":"wGWMbbcOge8ZB6rK8HZQdw","children":[{"id":"251","parent":"250","text":"NAC <8h post-ingesta → efectividad cercana al 100%, NO RETRASAR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"250","text":"Carbón activado <4h → única medida de descontaminación recomendada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"250","text":"Protocolo SNAP (2 bolsas/12h) → menos RAM y menor estancia que protocolo 21h tradicional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"250","text":"Nomograma SOLO válido para ingesta aguda única entre 4-24h post-ingesta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"250","text":"En AM la sobredosis REPETIDA supraterapéutica es más común que la aguda","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"250","text":"Paracetamol indetectable NO descarta hepatotoxicidad si presentación tardía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"250","text":"Lactato precoz elevado → marcador de severidad y posible toxicidad intestinal directa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"250","text":"NO suspender NAC por reacción anafilactoide leve → tratar y continuar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"250","text":"Fomepizole es adyuvante prometedor en sobredosis masiva o presentación tardía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"250","text":"En AM frágil considerar máximo 2g/día y revisar TODOS los OTC del hogar","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"261","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"262","parent":"261","text":"1. Dart RC, Mullins ME, Matoushek T, et al. Management of Acetaminophen Poisoning in the US and Canada: A Consensus Statement. JAMA Netw Open. 2023;6(8):e2327739. DOI: 10.1001/jamanetworkopen.2023.27739","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"261","text":"2. Chiew AL, Gluud C, Brok J, Buckley NA. Interventions for paracetamol (acetaminophen) overdose. Cochrane Database Syst Rev. 2018;2(2):CD003328. DOI: 10.1002/14651858.CD003328.pub3","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"261","text":"3. Hodgman MJ, Garrard AR. A review of acetaminophen poisoning. Crit Care Clin. 2012;28(4):499-516. DOI: 10.1016/j.ccc.2012.07.006","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"261","text":"4. Gosselin S, Juurlink DN, Kielstein JT, et al. Extracorporeal treatment for acetaminophen poisoning: recommendations from the EXTRIP workgroup. Clin Toxicol. 2014;52(8):856-67. DOI: 10.3109/15563650.2014.946994","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"261","text":"5. Yarema M, Chopra P, Sivilotti MLA, et al. Anaphylactoid Reactions to IV N-Acetylcysteine during Treatment for Acetaminophen Poisoning. J Med Toxicol. 2018;14(2):120-127. DOI: 10.1007/s13181-018-0653-9","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"261","text":"6. Supervía A, Gispert MA, Puiguriguer J, et al. Paracetamol poisoning: a prospective comparison of 2 protocols for NAC treatment. Emergencias. 2025;37(1):39-43. DOI: 10.55633/s3me/100.2024","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"261","text":"7. Cole JB, Oakland CL, Lee SC, et al. Two-bag IV NAC Regimens for Acetaminophen Poisoning: A Systematic Review. West J Emerg Med. 2023;24(6):1131-1145. DOI: 10.5811/westjem.59099","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"261","text":"8. Chen F, Lu SZ, Choha H, Lau A. The Role of Fomepizole in Acetaminophen-related Poisoning: A Narrative Review. Clin Exp Emerg Med. 2025. DOI: 10.15441/ceem.25.059","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"261","text":"9. Codinach-Martín M, Ortega-Pérez J, Gispert-Ametller MA, et al. N-acetylcysteine as antidote for paracetamol poisoning: a multicenter study. Emergencias. 2022;34(3):190-195","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"261","text":"10. Perananthan V, Shihana F, Chiew AL, et al. Intestinal injury in paracetamol overdose (ATOM-8). J Gastroenterol Hepatol. 2024;39(5):920-926. DOI: 10.1111/jgh.16450","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"261","text":"11. Wolf SJ, Heard K, Sloan EP, Jagoda AS. ACEP Clinical Policy: Acetaminophen Overdose. Ann Emerg Med. 2007;50(3):292-313. DOI: 10.1016/j.annemergmed.2007.06.014","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"261","text":"12. Motohashi K, Thanacoody RH. Toxicology in the emergency department: what's new? Br J Hosp Med. 2022;83(9):1-16. DOI: 10.12968/hmed.2022.0313","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":273,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Urgencias","filename":"IntoxicacionParacetamol iPad","id":"map_2368","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"IntoxicacionParacetamol iPad"}